  "prompt": "Which are the best colleges or universities for automobile engineering in India?",
  "response": "India is home to several prestigious institutions that offer excellent programs in automobile engineering. Here are some of the top colleges and universities known for their automobile engineering courses:\n\n1. **Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Madras** - Known for its rigorous curriculum and research facilities in automotive engineering.\n\n2. **Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Delhi** - Offers advanced research opportunities and has strong industry connections.\n\n3. **Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bombay** - Renowned for its engineering programs and extensive research initiatives in the field of automobile engineering.\n\n4. **Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Kharagpur** - Offers comprehensive programs in automotive engineering with a focus on innovation and technology development.\n\n5. **Vellore Institute of Technology (VIT), Vellore** - Offers specialized programs in automobile engineering and collaborates with industry leaders for practical training.\n\n6. **Manipal Institute of Technology (MIT), Manipal** - Known for its quality education and strong emphasis on practical learning in automobile engineering.\n\n7. **National Institute of Technology (NIT) Trichy** - Offers robust programs in mechanical engineering with a specialization in automobile engineering.\n\n8. **Birla Institute of Technology and Science (BITS), Pilani** - Provides excellent academic and research opportunities in the field of automotive engineering.\n\n9. **College of Engineering, Pune (COEP)** - One of the oldest engineering colleges in India, offering specialized courses in automobile engineering.\n\n10. **SRM Institute of Science and Technology, Chennai** - Known for its comprehensive curriculum and industry-oriented training in automobile engineering.\n\nThese institutions are recognized for their strong academic programs, research facilities, industry connections, and overall contribution to the field of automobile engineering in India.",
